<h2>Chapter 3: Step 1. Choose and Define Your Topic Niche &#123;#ch3&#125;</h2>
<p>The most common topical authority mistake: picking a topic too broad to own.</p>
<p>"Marketing" is not a topic. "Content marketing for B2B SaaS" is a topic. "Email marketing for e-commerce brands" is a topic. The narrower your niche, the faster you reach full coverage and the faster Google recognizes authority.</p>
