Each major subtopic becomes either a detailed cluster page or a mini-hub if the subtopic is large enough to have its own sub-cluster.</p>
<p><strong>Level 3: Specific Articles (Cluster Pages)</strong>
Targeted long-tail keywords under each subtopic.</p>
