<td>Cluster page</td>
<td>Pillar</td>
<td>"complete guide to content SEO"</td>
<td>"this guide"</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Cluster A</td>
<td>Cluster B</td>
<td>"long-tail keyword strategy"</td>
<td>"read more here"</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Cluster page</td>
