</tr>
</tbody>
</table></div>
<p>Building quality <a href="/blog/blog-seo/">blog SEO</a> practices. Including internal linking. Into your publishing workflow saves hours of retroactive linking later. Add the pillar link and 2 sibling links before you hit publish. Never after.</p>
